ReferenceDocuments.name: A questionnaire to assess eat
ReferenceDocuments.description: A questionnaire to assess eating disorders including Anorexia Nervosa, which is a refusal to maintain normal weight, and Bulimia Nervosa characterized by episodes of binge eating followed by vomiting, use of laxatives, or fasting. Anorexia Nervosa and Bulimia Nervosa are accompanied by unhealthy attitudes about body shape and weight
